<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ARENA-X Password Reset</title>
    <style>
        /* Cyberpunk Email Styles */
        :root {
            --blood-red: #ff0000;
            --dark-red: #8b0000;
            --neon-red: #ff003c;
            --black-hole: #000000;
            --metal-gray: #111111;
            --carbon-gray: #222222;
            --toxic-purple: #9d00ff;
        }
        
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: var(--black-hole);
            font-family: 'Orbitron', 'Rajdhani', 'Arial', sans-serif;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #0a0a0a 100%);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,0,60,0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(255,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .email-header {
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--neon-red);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .email-header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--neon-red), var(--toxic-purple), transparent);
            animation: scan 2s linear infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes scan {
            0% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
            100% { transform: translateX(100%); }
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-family: 'Aldrich', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: transparent;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--blood-red), var(--neon-red));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,0,60,0.5);
            margin: 0;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
        }
        
        .logo-sub {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        .email-body {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        .greeting::before {
            content: '>';
            color: var(--neon-red);
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #ccc;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .reset-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--dark-red), var(--neon-red));
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            border: none;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,0,60,0.5);
        }
        
        .reset-button::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent);
            transition: 0.5s;
        }
        
        .reset-button:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }
        
        .reset-button span {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        .reset-link-container {
            background: rgba(255,0,60,0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,0,60,0.3);
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .reset-link-label {
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: var(--neon-red);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .reset-link {
            font-family: 'Aldrich', monospace;
            word-break: break-all;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
        
        .expiry-notice {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--neon-red);
            margin: 30px 0;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #999;
        }
        
        .expiry-notice strong {
            color: var(--neon-red);
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .signature {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,0,60,0.3);
        }
        
        .signature-line {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .signature-arena {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: transparent;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--neon-red), var(--toxic-purple));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .email-footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,0,60,0.2);
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        
        .footer-text {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .glitch-effect {
            animation: glitch 3s infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes glitch {
            0%, 100% { transform: skew(0deg, 0deg); }
            95% { transform: skew(0deg, 0deg); }
            96% { transform: skew(5deg, 0deg); opacity: 0.8; }
            97% { transform: skew(-5deg, 0deg); opacity: 0.9; }
            98% { transform: skew(3deg, 0deg); opacity: 0.8; }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 10px;
            }
            
            .reset-button {
                display: block;
                padding: 15px 20px;
                font-size: 1em;
            }
            
            .logo {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1 class="logo">ARENA-X</h1>
            <div class="logo-sub">ELITE GAMING DIVISION</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-body">
            <h2 class="greeting">OPERATOR ACCESS</h2>
            
            <p class="message">
                A password reset request has been initiated for your account. 
                Click the secure link below to regain access to your command center.
            </p>
            
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{ resetUrl }}" class="reset-button">
                    <span>RESET ACCESS ⚡</span>
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="reset-link-container">
                <div class="reset-link-label">DIRECT ACCESS CODE:</div>
                <div class="reset-link">{{ resetUrl }}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="expiry-notice">
                <strong>⚠ SECURITY PROTOCOL:</strong> This access link will self-destruct in 
                <strong>1 HOUR</strong>. Request a new one if it expires.
            </div>
            
            <div class="signature">
                <div class="signature-line">Stay dangerous,</div>
                <div class="signature-arena">ARENA-X COMMAND</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p class="footer-text">
                This is an automated message from ARENA-X. Do not reply to this email.
                If you didn't request this, please secure your account immediately.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>